INTENT

This software was built for vehicle owners — specifically the right to service,
diagnose, and modify the electronic systems in their own property.

If you are a dealership, independent repair shop, or any person or entity
intending to use this tool commercially (including charging others for CP
removal, ECU tuning, or related services), this license does not prohibit that
— but know that this tool was not built for you. It was built for the people
sitting in the waiting room of your service department while you charge them
$400 to do a 10-minute software operation.

The GPL v3 ensures that any modified version of this tool must also be free and
open. You cannot take this code, make it proprietary, and sell it. That is the
only commercial restriction. The full license text follows.

